%% seq_02a_task_create_update.mmd
%% Scope: Create and update task authoring flow.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Project Manager
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Entity as TaskEntity
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: CREATE TASK
    U->>B: Fill create task form
    B->>C: POST /tasks
    C->>Cmd: CreateTaskCommand
    Cmd->>Cmd: Validate org + project permission
    Cmd->>Entity: Build new task aggregate
    Cmd->>Repo: save(task)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT tasks
    Cmd->>Evt: emit(task:created)
    C-->>B: Redirect to detail

    Note over U, Evt: UPDATE TASK
    U->>B: Edit task fields
    B->>C: PUT /tasks/:id
    C->>Cmd: UpdateTaskCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: findById(taskId)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT task
    Repo-->>Cmd: Task aggregate
    Cmd->>Entity: Apply field changes
    Cmd->>Repo: save(task)
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE tasks
    Cmd->>Repo: saveVersion(snapshot)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT task_versions
    Cmd->>Evt: emit(task:updated)
    C-->>B: Redirect back
